This is my first git repo

finding address from geo location using google map

multi page form in laravel using html and javascript

To implement the functionality of email verfication after registration check out the following files:
1)AuthRegistrationController.php (in actual folder view Auth/RegistrationController.php).
2)LoginController.php (Controller/LoginController).
3)VerifyMail
4)login.blade.php
5)web.php(                  Route::get('/user/verify/{token}', 'Auth\RegisterController@verifyUser');          )
6)mail.blade.php

for more details refer to the 5ballons( https://www.5balloons.info/user-email-verification-and-account-activation-in-laravel-5-5/ ).


add this function to the User model
public function verifyUser(){
        return $this->hasOne('App\VerifyUser');
    }

add this function to the VerifyMail Model
public function user(){
    	return $this->belongsTo('App\User','user_id');
    }


install guzzle using

composer require guzzlehttp/guzzle


Changes to be done in ResetPassword Laravel 5.5
vendor/laravel/framework/src/Illuminate/Auth/Notifications/ResetPassword.php


